\ls1\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Today\'85I\'92m going to encourage you to walk down a different street\'85to avoid the obvious hole in the street we are all walking down\'85but there is a problem.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The reality is that while I\'92m going to spend the next several minutes trying to convince to avoid a huge pot hole\'85you\'92re to live out what we talked about last week.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}If you were here last week you know we talked about the ability we all posses to hear the word of God, listen to what it says, and then deceive ourselves by not doing it.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}And then in turn what we said was it is really easy to end up in a place where you are looking at the mirror asking\'85how did I get here?\
\pard\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\slleading24\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
