\ls2\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}As a nation we are on more medications than ever before\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We have crime rates that seem higher than ever before\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}School shootings\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Depression and anxiety are at all time highs\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Energy seems to be at an all time low - this has been enhanced by the addition of energy drinks\
\pard\tx220\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\li720\fi-720\slleading24\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 	\'95	Something is wrong and every day more and more people wake up, look in the mirror and ask\'85how did I get here?\
\pard\tx220\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\li720\fi-720\slleading24\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}But you don\'92t have to do\'85there is a way to avoid ALL of this\'85but as I said\'85you\'92re not going to like, you\'92re going to excuse it\'85and the reality is you\'92re probably going to think what God\'92s solution for this is just too extreme and won\'92t work.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}But here goes my best effort to get to start to adopt Disciplines that make a Difference.\
\pard\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\slleading24\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
