\ls4\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Now to set this up\'85you need to understand something..the 10 Commandments are those given to God\'92s people for them to be different.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}God is giving them a list of things to do and not do so they could live at peace vertically and horizontally.\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\li1440\fi-1440\slleading24\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	
\f2 \uc0\u8259 
\f1 	}Both WITH God and WITH others.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\li720\fi-720\slleading24\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}And, maybe you\'92ve never thought about them before but they are in order of importance.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Meaning God starts with most important and goes down the list from there.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}For those who haven\'92t got them memorized here is the list\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\li1440\fi-1440\slleading24\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	
\f2 \uc0\u8259 
\f1 	}You shall have no other gods \
{\listtext	
\f2 \uc0\u8259 
\f1 	}You shall not make idols\
{\listtext	
\f2 \uc0\u8259 
\f1 	}You shall not take God\'92s name in vain\
{\listtext	
\f2 \uc0\u8259 
\f1 	}Remember the Sabbath day, and keep it holy\
{\listtext	
\f2 \uc0\u8259 
\f1 	}Honor your father and your mother\
{\listtext	
\f2 \uc0\u8259 
\f1 	}You shall not murder\
{\listtext	
\f2 \uc0\u8259 
\f1 	}You shall not commit adultery\
{\listtext	
\f2 \uc0\u8259 
\f1 	}You shall not steal\
{\listtext	
\f2 \uc0\u8259 
\f1 	}You shall not lie\
{\listtext	
\f2 \uc0\u8259 
\f1 	}You shall not covet\
\pard\tx220\tx720\tx1120\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\li720\fi-720\slleading24\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}And if you\'92re being honest...this list doesn\'92t look like it is order does it?\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Come on...no one in here thinks murder is less important to do or not than remembering the sabbath day...anyone?  I didn\'92t think so?\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I told you...what I\'92m talking about today is not obvious or intuitive...\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It\'92s different...it\'92s complex\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}And I don\'92t think what God is saying is that if someone forgets the sabbath they are worse than a murderer...that\'92s not the point. The point is this\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Our 
